{
    "text": "ChatGPT is my CSS advisor",
    "created": "Thu, 21 Dec 2023 17:56:50 GMT",
    "type": "outline",
    "subs": [
        {
            "text": "People who don't program must not have any idea how much of a boon ChatGPT is to us programmers. ",
            "created": "Thu, 21 Dec 2023 17:57:28 GMT",
            "flInCalendar": true
        },
        {
            "text": "I am doing <a href=\"https://www.w3schools.com/css/\">CSS</a> coding far in advance of my previous capability. When I know something is possible, but I haven't the slightest idea how to specify it, I just ask, in my own words. ",
            "created": "Thu, 21 Dec 2023 17:57:50 GMT",
            "flInCalendar": true
        },
        {
            "text": "For example, a very common thing to want to do is to put a : after the text in the first column every row of a table. ",
            "created": "Thu, 21 Dec 2023 17:58:19 GMT",
            "flInCalendar": true
        },
        {
            "text": "So I <a href=\"https://chat.openai.com/share/b19c1c8d-3e19-4039-86aa-803eb7cf46d6\">asked ChatGPT</a> how to do it, in English, as I did above. This is what it came up with:",
            "created": "Thu, 21 Dec 2023 17:54:03 GMT",
            "type": "outline",
            "subs": [
                {
                    "text": "<code>tr td:first-child::after {content: \":\";}</code>",
                    "created": "Thu, 21 Dec 2023 17:55:57 GMT",
                    "flInCalendar": true
                }
            ],
            "flInCalendar": true
        },
        {
            "text": "When you see it like that you can almost figure out what's going on if you squint and close one eye. ",
            "created": "Thu, 21 Dec 2023 17:58:45 GMT",
            "flInCalendar": true
        },
        {
            "text": "And it works. I literally shrieked when it did. ",
            "created": "Thu, 21 Dec 2023 17:58:57 GMT",
            "flInCalendar": true
        },
        {
            "text": "Now I am the boss of CSS.. ",
            "created": "Thu, 21 Dec 2023 17:59:09 GMT",
            "flInCalendar": true
        },
        {
            "text": "Nice.",
            "created": "Thu, 21 Dec 2023 17:59:21 GMT",
            "flInCalendar": true
        }
    ],
    "flInCalendar": true
}